Package: mSigPlot
Title: Mutational signature plotting functions
Version: 1.0.4
Authors@R: 
    person("Steven", "Rozen", , "steverozen@pm.me", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: mSigPlot stands for Mutational Signature Plotting. Provides
   functions for mutational signatures and mutational spectra including 
   single base substitutions (SBS), doublet base substitutions (DBS), and
   small insertions and deletions (indels).
License: GPL (>= 3)
